         <div subtype="original" type="letter" xml:id="L.1932" xml:lang="en">
            <pb facs="#IMG.1" n="1"/>
            <dateline>Colombo, 2 July 1890</dateline>
            <opener>My dear Sir,</opener>
            <p>By this mail I send you copies of a few Caffrinha songs, sent me by Mr <persName ref="[authorityLink]">W Goonetilleke</persName> of Kandy, who got the originals from a certain Solomon Christian. This man wrote them down, but all mixed up, and Mr <persName ref="[authorityLink]">G</persName> had some trouble in copying them out. I hope they will be of use to you.</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>Yours very truly</salute>
               <lb/>
               <signed>
                  <persName ref="[authorityLink]">Donald Ferguson</persName>
               </signed>
            </closer>
            <pb facs="#IMG.2" n="2"/>
         </div>
